title: United Kingdom Imports of Silk
description: Imports of Silk in the United Kingdom increased to 2.14 GBP Million in September from 1.92 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Silk in the United Kingdom averaged 3.14 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 4.91 GBP Million in July of 2007 and a record low of 0.77 GBP Million in December of 2020. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Silk.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
